{"tid":2489802,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"本地創投企業家 投資 *[*6億+*]*  購6,676呎山頂項目, 呎價9萬","createTime":"2021-04-15T07:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T07:33:24.000Z","uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6bc6159da5897c7466c730d0518936532a38c3","tid":2489802,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:33:24.000Z","msg":"由九龍倉持有、並由會德豐地產發展及銷售的山頂項目77/79 Peak Road 上月公布售出2幢洋房，其中77B Peak Road售價逾<ins><strong>6億元</strong></ins>，實用面積6,676平方呎，花園面積2,947平方呎，停車位面積1,181平方呎，<ins><strong>呎價約9萬元</strong></ins>。土地註冊處資料顯示，新買家為方仁宙（ALEXANDER）及陳英珮（ JOSEPHINE），其中方仁宙為本地著名創投企業家，2017年創辦海闊天空創投基金（Beyond Ventures），投資港產初創企業。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2932508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2932508&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=2f6b3a1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2932508</a>"}]}